Mexico Plans to Implement Program to Refinance States’ Debt, Cordero Says

-- B y   C a r l o s   M a n u e l   R o d r i g u e z
-- 
2011-08-14T23:11:56Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-14/mexico-plans-to-implement-program-to-refinance-states-debt-cordero-says.html
Mexico  plans to announce this week a
program to refinance debt of some states, the country’s Finance
Minister  Ernesto Cordero  said today in a webcast message.  A Mexican development bank known as Banobras will
participate in the program, Cordero said without offering
details.  Mexico will also announce this coming week a program to
help small businesses, Cordero said, to fuel domestic demand.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Carlos Manuel Rodriguez in Mexico City at 
 carlosmr@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
